1.title: Net
1.definition: Net financial account (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

1452076605570.title: Assets
1452076605570.definition: Financial account assets (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

1452076612489.title: Liabilities
1452076612489.definition: Financial account liabilities (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

1452077490778.title: Net
1452077490778.definition: Net financial account, direct investment (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

1452077529556.title: Liabilities

1452077585632.title: Net
1452077585632.definition: Net financial account, portfolio investment (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

1452077591544.title: Assets
1452077591544.definition: Financial account, portfolio investment assets (transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards).

c1542702636664.title: Net ratio
c1542702636664.definition: Net financial account as percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (assets minus liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 and ESA 2010 standards).

c1542702638198.title: Assets ratio
c1542702638198.definition: Financial account assets as percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (assets, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards and ESA 2010 standards).

c1542702639166.title: Liabilities ratio
c1542702639166.definition: Financial account liabilities as percentage of gross domestic product (GDP) at market prices (liabilities, transactions vis-à-vis non-residents; four-quarter cumulated; not seasonally or working day-adjusted; BPM6 standards and ESA 2010 standards).
